data.name: label11.Text
data.value: If you recieved an email that a ticket you raised was closed by a member of our IT Support Team without it being solved, this page lets you re-open your ticket, and your re-open ticket will be considered our highest priority.

data.name: label9.Text
data.value: This page allows you to ask our IT Support Team a question if you cannot find the solution to your problem via the frequently asked questions in the "Problem List" section or the categorized problem documents in the "Online Help" section.

data.name: label7.Text
data.value: This page will display a table documenting information about all of the tickets that you have raised. This includes the ID, urgency level, problem type and description of problem. You can track the status of your ticket here.

data.name: label4.Text
data.value: Please note that if you re-raise a ticket that was closed by our IT Support team because the answer to your problem can be found in either the "Online Help" section or "Problem List" section of this form, your ticket will be promptly closed and you will not be able to re-open it again.
